docs {
  # Get Unread Notifications

  Retrieves only unread notifications for the authenticated user.

  ## Query Parameters
  - `isRead`: Set to `false` to get only unread notifications
  - `page` (optional): Page number (0-indexed)
  - `size` (optional): Page size

  ## Use Case
  - Display unread notifications in a dropdown or notification center
  - Show what needs user's attention
}

